main event: A witness reported seeing two bright lights in the sky that blinked alternately, moving at a high speed on July 6, 1966.
interesting points: The lights were reported to be about 1,500 feet up and traveling at a terrific speed,The blinking pattern was described as white-green-white-green,The witness noted that there was no sound associated with the lights,The duration of the sighting was brief but seemed longer than a few seconds to the witness,The conclusion from the Air Force was that there was insufficient data for evaluation.
sighted object: two bright blinking lights in the sky
witness description: A civilian who reported seeing the lights and wrote to the Air Force.
